Schroders Set to Take Over Invista Property Fund, Times Reports

-- B y   G r a n t   S m i t h
-- 
2011-08-14T08:44:35Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-14/schroders-set-to-take-over-invista-property-fund-times-reports.html
Schroders Plc is set to take over
the running of the 370 million-pound ($602 million) Invista
Property Foundation Trust, the  Sunday Times reported , without
saying where it got the information.  The deal is likely to be announced this week, according to
the newspaper. Duncan Owen will continue to run the fund as part
of a small team within Schroders, the Times said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Grant Smith in  London  at 
 gsmith52@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Stephen Voss on   sev@bloomberg.net  